### 서버 상태 확인
GET http://localhost:8080/health

### 회원가입
POST http://localhost:8080/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "newuser@example.com",
  "password": "Password123!",
  "name": "New User"
}

### 로그인
POST http://localhost:8080/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "newuser@example.com",
  "password": "Password123!"
}

### 토큰 갱신
POST http://localhost:8080/auth/refresh
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "refreshToken": "{{refreshToken}}"
}

### 구글 소셜 로그인 (idToken 은 클라이언트에서 획득) 아직 미구현
POST http://localhost:8080/auth/google
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "idToken": "{{googleIdToken}}"
}

### 카카오 소셜 로그인 (accessToken 은 카카오 SDK 에서 획득)  아직 미구현
POST http://localhost:8080/auth/kakao
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "accessToken": "{{kakaoAccessToken}}"
}

### Firebase 로그인 (Firebase Auth 로 받아온 ID Token 사용)
POST http://localhost:8080/auth/firebase
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "idToken": "{{firebaseIdToken}}"
}

### 내 정보 확인 (Authorization 헤더에 Access Token 필요)
GET http://localhost:8080/users/me
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

### 내 정보 수정
PATCH http://localhost:8080/users/me
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Updated User Name"
}

### 비밀번호 변경
PATCH http://localhost:8080/users/me/password
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "currentPassword": "Password123!",
  "newPassword": "NewPassword123!"
}

### 관리자 - 전체 유저 조회
GET http://localhost:8080/admin/users
Authorization: Bearer {{adminAccessToken}}
